  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<em>You are adept at increasing the range, area, and accuracy of splash weapons.</em><br/><br/><b>Benefits</b><br/>When throwing a splash weapon, you act as if you had the Far Shot feat. When you hit with a splash weapon, select one additional square adjacent to the splash area; creatures in this area also take splash damage. When you miss with a splash weapon, you may adjust the miss direction on the grid by +1 or -1. This feat counts as Far Shot for the purpose of qualifying for other feats, but only in regard to splash weapons.",
